display_long_description:
Calico Inc is a chaotic, thrilling multiplayer survival game where teamwork is your only shot at making it out alive. Trapped inside a bizarre corporate facility crawling with horrifying monsters, you and your friends must complete a series of bizarre and sometimes hilarious tasks — all while being hunted by relentless, unpredictable creatures that stalk the halls.

Every level is a wild mix of tension and laughter as you juggle objectives, manage limited resources, and scream (or laugh uncontrollably) when someone inevitably attracts the monster’s attention. Whether you’re stealthily sneaking past danger or sacrificing a teammate (for the greater good, of course), no two rounds ever play out the same.

Gather your squad, gear up, and get ready to run. Welcome to Calico Inc. Don’t get eaten.
